'Murica Memes

 

Once a month we will host competitions where users are able to submit their favorite ‘Murica memes. We suggest contestants be as creative as possible. The first two weeks of every month contestants will submit their favorite ‘Murica memes directly to us. After memes are verified and sent to murica.org MURC holders will be able to vote on their favorite memes posted by members of the community. At the end of each month, we will tally up the votes and distribute FREE MURC Coins to the highest voted MEME of the month. This is a great opportunity for fellow ‘Muricans to demonstrate their creativity and love of ‘Murica and it’s plethora of memes.

​

AND HEY WHO DOESN'T LOVE FREE MONEY???
